      "span_text": "The infarct areas of each slice were determined using a computerized image analyzer (Image-Pro plus). These areas were then summed and multiplied by the slice thickness to give the infarct volumes of each slice, which were calculated according to the method reported by Hsiao's group [CITATION_1] ."
